heading: 3. Where a person wishes to purchase a hard copy map or publication
text_raw:
3. Where a person wishes to purchase a hard copy map or publication 
specified in column 2 of Part 1 of Schedule 1, the fee specified in column 3 of 
that Part shall be payable to Tailte Éireann in respect of the item specified in 
column 2 of that Part opposite that fee so specified.

heading: 4. Where a person wishes to bulk purchase any 250 or more hard copy
text_raw:
4. Where a person wishes to bulk purchase any 250 or more hard copy 
maps (other than Compás Personalised Maps) or publications specified in 
column 2 of Part 1 of Schedule 1, the fee payable to Tailte Éireann shall be 
calculated in accordance with the discount specified in column 3 of Part 2 of 
Schedule 1 in respect of the number of items specified in column 2 of that Part 
opposite the discount so specified.

title: Title of Minister) Order 2023 (S.I. No. 19 of 2023)), hereby order as follows:
heading: 11. Where a person wishes to publish data contained in a map or product
text_raw:
11. Where a person wishes to publish data contained in a map or product 
specified in Part 1 of Schedule 1 or Part 3 or 4 of Schedule 2 in a manner 
described in column 2 of Part 7 of Schedule 2, the royalty fee shall be 
calculated by multiplying the amount specified in column 3 of that Part, 
opposite the description in column 2 of that Part, by the total number of copies 
to be published and that royalty fee shall be payable to Tailte Éireann, subject 
to a minimum royalty fee of €35 payable in respect of any request to publish.

title: Title of Minister) Order 2023 (S.I. No. 19 of 2023)), hereby order as follows:
heading: 12. Subject to Article 13, where a person wishes to enter a data licence
text_raw:
12. Subject to Article 13, where a person wishes to enter a data licence 
agreement with Tailte Éireann, the fee specified in column 3 of Schedule 3 
shall be payable to Tailte Éireann in respect of the first year of any such 
agreement and the fee specified in column 4 of Schedule 3 shall be payable to 
Tailte Éireann for every subsequent year of such agreement, in respect of the 
data set specified in column 2 of that Schedule opposite that fee so specified.
text_norm: 12 subject article 13 person wish enter data licence agreement tailte eireann fee specified column 3 schedule 3 shall payable tailte eireann respect first year agreement fee specified column 4 schedule 3 shall payable tailte eireann every subsequent year agreement respect data set specified column 2 schedule opposite fee specified

text_raw:

one or more data sets specified in row 1, 4, 5, 6 or 7 of column 2 of Schedule 3, 
the combined data sets included in that agreement shall be in respect of an area 
of at least 50 square kilometres.
